column3: Automatic sanity-testing: PASSED, see http://jenkins.bluematt.me/pull-tester/1c20eb2cfc2b55ae9ba4b1a1d596ec43814a9d34 for binaries and test log.\nThis test script verifies pulls every time they are updated. It, however, dies sometimes and fails to test properly.  If you are waiting on a test, please check timestamps to verify that the test.log is moving at http://jenkins.bluematt.me/pull-tester/cu

Fouten in de vertaling kan je het beste corrigeren op transifex (zie https://www.transifex.com/projects/p/bitcoin/ ). We importeren de vertalingen eens in de zoveel tijd vanuit daar, en dat overschrijft de bestanden in git.\n
